defaultProps.briefBiography: Dr. Kara Dioniso is a leader in the field of menopause practice and she is regularly invited to speak to naturopathic doctors across North America. Dr. Kara Dionisio is a NAMS-certified menopause practitioner since 2020 and holds an IMPART Menopause Certificate and a level 1 training in Pelvic Floor Physiotherapy. across North America.
